name: Tipboxcoin
description: Tipbox coin aims to be a safe investment tool that allows the service industry to be fully integrated into the blockchain system.  Tipbox coin will continue on its way by establishing new teams that will improve itself every day in order to be a fast and safe system in terms of structure.  The coin, which will make a lot of distribution for social responsibility projects, will serve not only as a tool for the service sector, but also for specified purposes.  When a received coin is sent to the business, it is distributed equally to the employees, while it is designed as a 2% donation system to charity foundations.
